e%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221598%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bar%20chart%20graphic%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley's%202025%20Summer%20Intern%20Survey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b8951a32af4d666ef72ef4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22846%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBar%20chart%20graphic%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley's%202025%20Summer%20Intern%20Survey.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%202025%20Summer%20Intern%20Survey%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20the%20Morgan%20Stanley%20interns%20(52%25)%20reported%20personally%20subscribing%20to%20the%20paid%20version%20of%20an%20AI%20tool.%20About%2048%25%20said%20they%20have%20paid%20for%20ChatGPT%2C%20reiterating%20the%20tool's%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20use%20AI%20for%20work%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20in%20their%20personal%20lives%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22women%20beach%20vacation%20swimming%20water%20summer%20suntan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F592d9b3d79474cbd1b8b4f12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Foto%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20part%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20interns%20were%20asked%20how%20and%20what%20they%20use%20ChatGPT%20for.%20The%20most%20common%20uses%20were%20work-related.%20About%2079%25%20of%20interns%20said%20they%20use%20it%20to%20learn%20about%20a%20new%20topic%20and%20summarize%20long%20pieces%20of%20text.%20The%20other%20most%20common%20usages%20of%20the%20tool%20are%20drafting%2Fediting%20emails%20or%20other%20texts%20(74%25)%20and%20writing%2C%20programming%2C%20or%20debugging%20code%20(56%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20interns%20also%20use%20ChatGPT%20for%20personal%20tasks%3A%20About%2045%25%20said%20they%20ask%20it%20for%20personal%20advice%20and%20help%20planning%20a%20vacation.%20About%2036%25%20use%20it%20to%20find%20recipes