em%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22845ff874-9168-4599-a373-e276214af899%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20I'm%20offering%20AI%20researchers%20%242%20million%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20because%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-salary-divide-meta-microsoft-layoffs-100-million-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etalent%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20started%20by%20Mark%20Zuckerberg.%20I%20used%20to%20work%20at%20Meta%2C%20and%20I%20speak%20with%20my%20former%20colleagues%20often%20about%20this.%20When%20I%20heard%20about%20their%20compensation%20packages%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20really%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20millions%20range.%20But%20it%20shows%20that%20in%20this%20age%2C%20AI%20researchers%20who%20make%20the%20best%20models%20and%20stand%20at%20the%20frontier%20of%20technology%20are%20really%20worth%20this%20amount%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20building%20an%20AI%20model%20that%20can%20see%20and%20remember%20just%20like%20humans.%20The%20things%20that%20we%20are%20working%20on%20are%20very%20niche.%20So%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20people%20who%20are%20really%2C%20really%20good%20at%20the%20whole%20field%20of%20understanding%20video%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227bd31608-bcff-4f78-ad04-6bb2d69cc7fb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20not%20worried%20about%20running%20out%20of%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20welcoming%20people%20who%20want%20to%20take%20more%20equity%20compared%20to%20cash%2C%20which%20means%20that%20it%20won't%20shrink%20our%20runway%20by%20a%20huge%20amount.%20The%20exact%20cash-versus-equity%20split%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20person%20we%20hire.%20We%20will%20treat%20these%20hires%20as%20founding%20members%2C%20not%20as%20employees.%20Anyways%2C%20equity%20is%20where%20you%20can%20get%20a%20hundred%20or%20even%20a%20thousand%20times%20return%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20thinking%20of%20hiring%20three%20to%20five%20people%20in%20the%20next%206%20months%2C%20and%20another%20five%20to%20ten%20in%20the%20next%2012%20months.%20We%20plan%20to%20raise%20more%20money%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a94409d8-13a5-442c-b37c-8317633c776f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpending%20so%20much%20on%20talent%20will%20help%2C%20not%20hurt%2C%20our%20fundraising%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20consistently%20attract%20top%20AI%20talent%2C%20raising%20additional%20capital%20will%20not%20be%20a%20problem.%20The%20capital%20markets%20are%20eager%20to%20back%20companies%20that%20can%20do%20this.%20Just%20look%20at%20how%20much%20Thinking%20Machines%20Labs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmira-murati-new-ai-startup-thinking-machines-funding-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehas%20raised%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20how%20much%20Fei-Fei%20Li's%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldlabs.ai%2Fabout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20raised%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20long%20as%20an%20AI%20company%20can%20recruit%20the%20best%20AI%20people%2C%20they%20can%20really%20just%20go%20through%20any%20kind%20of%20economic%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9e47561-acdb-41e0-a984-84d94ee9bd4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeta's%20constant%20reorgs%20help%20our%20hiring%20efforts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20constantly%20doing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-superintelligence-labs-reorg-alexandr-wang-memo-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereorganizations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Your%20manager%20and%20your%20goals%20can%20change%20every%20few%20months.%20For%20some%20researchers%2C%20it%20can%20be%20really%20frustrating%20and%20feel%20like%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%20So%20yes%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20driver%20for%20people%20to%20leave%20Meta%20and%20join%20other%20companies%2C%20especially%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20other%20reasons%20people%20might%20