ht%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20market%20correction.%20A%20wake-up%20call.%20A%20great%20digestion.%20Call%20it%20what%20you%20want%3A%20AI%20is%20going%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20things%20appear%20to%20be%20happening%20in%20tandem.%20Businesses%20are%20starting%20to%20finally%20grasp%20what%20AI%20can%20%E2%80%94%20and%20importantly%2C%20can't%20%E2%80%94%20do%20to%20boost%20their%20bottom%20lines.%20And%20the%20sky-high%20expectations%20that%20have%20been%20partly%20inflated%20and%20overhyped%20by%20AI%20firms%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20are%20finally%20coming%20down%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20it's%20increasingly%20looking%20like%20both%20the%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flimits-large-language-models-chatgpt-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-openai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoomers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20boomers%20were%20both%20wrong.%20AI's%20trajectory%20is%20starting%20to%20look%20less%20like%20a%20time%20machine%20or%20space%20elevator%20and%20more%20akin%20computers%2C%20smartphones%2C%20televisions%3A%20The%20technology%20will%20get%20better%2C%20it%20will%20almost%20certainly%20change%20our%20lives%20in%20the%20fullness%20of%20time%2C%20but%20it%20will%20more%20likely%20do%20so%20incrementally%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20point%20that%20if%20AGI%20(artificial%20general%20intelligence)%20or%20superintelligence%20do%20in%20fact%20one%20day%20arrive%2C%20it%20might%20not%20seem%20like%20much%20of%20a%20leap%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20perhaps%20no%20better%20example%20of%20this%20happening%20than%20OpenAI's%20latest%20and%20long-anticipated%20model%2C%20GPT-5%2C%20which%20was%20touted%20with%20a%20bang%20and%20landed%20with%20a%20shrug.%20Ahead%20of%20launch%2C%20OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20he'd%20felt%20%26quot%3Buseless%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20the%20model's%20intelligence%2C%20even%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20the%20Manhattan%20Project.%20When%20it%20arrived%2C%20users%20apparently%20felt%20less%20intimidated.%20%26quot%3BThe%20degree%20of%20overhyping%20was%20too%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20absence%20of%20massive%20gains%2C%20all%20you%20have%20is%20hype%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FOpenAI%2Fcomments%2F1mp4oow%2Fgpt5_is_pretty_good_actually_the_real_issue_is%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20another%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20may%20be%20a%20glimpse%20at%20our%20new%20reality%2C%20where%20the%20breakneck%20speed%20of%20AI%20progress%20is%20simply%20steadying%2C%20where%20progress%20cannot%20run%20on%20hype%20alone%2C%20and%20where%20we%20will%20neither%20experience%20an%20overnight%20white-collar%20job%20wipeout%20nor%20reach%20an%20AI%20abundance%20society%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20AI's%20%26quot%3Bmeh%26quot%3B%20era.%20Stay%20calm.%20We've%20been%20here%20before.%20It'll%20all%20be%20fine.%20Probably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20internet%20revolution%20took%20hold%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20companies%20were%20minting%20millions%20overnight%20with%20little%20more%20than%20a%20website%20and%20a%20savvy%20sales%20pitch.%20By%20the%20year%202000%2C%20the%20economic%20reality%20caught%20up%20to%20the%20hype%2C%20leaving%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20wiped%20out%20overnight.%20Not%20familiar%3F%20Go%20ask%20your%20parents%20what%20happened%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPets.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPets.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20talk%20of%20a%20bubble%20has%20once%20again%20reared%20its%20head.%20Even%20Altman%20recently%20(and%20in%20an%20unusually%20measured%20moment%20from%20AI's%20biggest%20hype%20man)%20said%20he%20believes%20the%20AI%20market%20might%20be%20in%20a%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20back%20to%20the%201990s%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-ai-bubble-boom-dotcom-interview-peter-kafka-2025-09%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edotcom%20bubble%20burst%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20weren't%20the%20profits%20necessarily%20to%20back%20the%20investments%20up%2C%20but%20there%20were%20tangible%20productivity%20gains%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Carl%20Benedikt%20Frey%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20Oxford.%20If%20that%20sounds%20eerily%20familiar%2C%20a%20check%20on%20AI%20now%20could%20prevent%20history%20from%20repeating%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20published%20by%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20further%20stirred%20the%20pot%20last%20month%2C%20claiming%20that%20just%205%25%20of%20companies%20it%20studied%20have%20managed%20to%20convert%20the%20technology%20into%20actual%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20a%20revelation%20scary%20enough%20to%20cause%20a%20tech%20stock%20sell-off%2C%20even%20if%20the%20study%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20evidence%20suggests%20AI%20is%20starting%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20businesses%20that%20are%20adopting%20it.%20A%20study%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitaleconomy.stanford.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FCanaries_BrynjolfssonChandarChen.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanford%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20researchers%20that%20analyzed%20payroll%20data%20concluded%20that%20AI%20was%20killing%20off%20entry-level%20jobs%20for%20people%20aged%2022%20to%2025%2C%20and%20was%20especially%20doing%20so%20in%20fields%20where%20AI%20was%20more%20likely%20to%20replace%2C%20rather%20than%20augment%2C%20labor.%20Marc%20Benioff%20claims%20AI%20agents%20are%20replacing%20thousands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff-says-salesforce-cut-4000-roles-because-of-agents-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalesforce's%20support%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20other%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-b2b-content-marketing-automation-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20boasting%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI%20automating%20more%20of%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20of%20AI's%20effects%20on%20the%20demand%20for%20foreign%20translators%20by%20Frey%20and%20fellow%20Oxford%20economist%20Pedro%20Llanos-Paredes%2C%20published%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20concluded%20that%20the%20technology%20was%20having%20a%20small%20but%20provable%20impact%20on%20these%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20seem%20to%20be%20seeing%20reasonable%20revenue%20growth%20for%20a%20handful%20of%20firms%20that%20are%20pioneering%20the%20AI%20revolution%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20seeing%20it%20translate%20into%20broader%20economic%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Frey%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20find%20concerning%20is%20that%20we're%20still%20not%20seeing%20any%20hint%20of%20it%20in%20the%20productivity%20statistics%2C%20and%20ultimately%20that's%20what%20matters.%20It%20doesn't%20really%20matter%20how%20well%20AI%20performs%20on%20tests%20or%20on%20some%20benchmark.%20What%20matters%20is%20translating%20that%20into%20real%20economic%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20markets%2C%20a%20more%20modest%20uptake%20may%20be%20perfectly%20OK.%20Evercore%20ISI%20strategists%20predict%20AI%20excitement%20will%20buoy%20US%20stocks%20a%20further%2020%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20'bigger'%20than%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20published%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BIn%20three%20years%2C%20its%20effect%20has%20touched%20all%20parts%20of%20society%20and%20industry%20even%20as%20adoption%20only%20begins%20to%20inflect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-nvda-stock-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20a%20strong%20indicator%20of%20where%20we're%20at.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20sells%20the%20valuable%20chips%20on%20which%20AI%20is%20trained%20and%20run%2C%20has%20become%20something%20of%20a%20bellwether%20for%20the%20entire%20artificial%20intelligence%20boom%20and%20counts%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20tech%20giants%20as%20key%20customers.%20(Bloomberg%20estimates%20that%20Microsoft%20spends%20about%2047%25%20of%20its%20capital%20expenditures%20on%20Nvidia's%20chips.)%20While%20it%20beat%20Wall%20Street%20expectations%20and%20its%20own%20sales%20records%2C%20its%20stock%20still%20dropped%2C%20suggesting%20investors%20weren't%20impressed%20with%20the%20figures%20they%20saw.%20Some%20analysts%20warn%20that%20the%20companies%20buying%20these%20services%20from%20Nvidia%20aren't%20yet%20seeing%20the%20returns.%20One%20UBS%20analyst%20characterized%20Nvidia's%20results%20in%20a%20way%20that%20may%20perfectly%20sum%20up%20the%20new%20steady-chug-along%20paradigm%20of%20AI%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2025-08-28%2Fnvidia-results-good-enough-to-keep-ai-trend-going-ubs-video%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bgood%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20to%20say%2C%20AI%20seems%20to%20have%20reached%20its%20iPhone%204%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Apple's%20iPhone%204%20arrived%20in%202010%2C%20it%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20smash%20hit.%20Onstage%20in%20Cupertino%2C%20Steve%20Jobs%20boasted%20that%20Apple%20had%20made%20the%20thinnest%20phone%20in%20the%20world%20with%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20new%20must-have%20features%3A%20a%20squared-off%20design%2C%20high-resolution%20display%2C%20a%20front-facing%20camera%20for%20FaceTime%20and%20selfies%2C%20and%20the%20debut%20of%20Apple's%20custom%20silicon%20chip%2C%20the%20A4.%20It%20flew%20off%20the%20shelves%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20the%20antenna%20fiasco%20%E2%80%94%20and%20further%20cemented%20Apple%20as%20the%20king%20of%20the%20smartphone.%20One%20could%20argue%20that%20the%20market%20has%20been%20chasing%20the%20iPhone%204's%20%26quot%3Bsandwich%20glass%26quot%3B%20design%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20things%20changed%3A%20With%20the%20exception%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20moderate%20leaps%20since%2C%20the%20iPhone%20has%20been%20on%20a%20more%20incremental%20trajectory.%20Evidence%20suggests%20artificial%20intelligence%20might%20be%20plotting%20a%20similar%20course.%20Frontier%20labs%20have%20been%20rolling%20out%20a%20steady%20flow%20of%20updates%20and%20mini-leaps%2C%20rather%20than%20waiting%20years%20between%20generations%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20each%20new%20rollout%20has%20started%20feeling%20evolutionary%2C%20incremental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20the%20leading%20expert%20in%20the%20field%2C%20I%20think%20the%20progress%20has%20been%20such%20that%20you%20probably%20won't%20even%20notice%20the%20improvements%20from%20now%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Frey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20big%20topic%20was%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-wall-scaling-laws-training-data-chatgpt-gemini-claude-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20labs%20were%20seeing%20diminishing%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20simply%20trying%20to%20throw%20more%20data%20and%20compute%20power%20at%20the%20models.%20That%20may%20go%20some%20way%20to%20explain%20how%20GPT-5%20landed%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20the%20launch%20of%20GPT-4%20in%20March%202023%20and%20GPT-5%20last%20month%2C%20OpenAI%20rolled%20out%20well%20over%20a%20dozen%20models%2C%20each%20one%20focusing%20on%20specific%20jobs%20or%20incrementally%20improving%20another.%20It's%20perhaps%20no%20wonder%2C%20then%2C%20that%20GPT-5%20didn't%20blow%20our%20socks%20off.%20(In%20the%20same%20conversation%20in%20which%20Altman%20claimed%20AI%20is%20in%20a%20bubble%2C%20he%20also%20claimed%20that%20OpenAI%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fcommand-line-newsletter%2F759897%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-social-media-google-chrome-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20advanced%20models%20than%20GPT-5%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20can't%20deploy%20them%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20capacity.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20latest%20frontier%20model%2C%20Gemini%202.5%2C%20is%20also%20a%20bridge%20model%2C%20and%20the%20launch%20of%20GPT-5%20may%20serve%20as%20a%20healthy%20warning%20to%20temper%20expectations%20for%20Gemini%203%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20before%20the%20year's%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20progress%20just%20feels%20more%20continuous%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20David%20Krueger%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Montreal%20who%20studies%20AI%20safety%20and%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrueger%20still%20thinks%20we'll%20have%20the%20occasional%20%26quot%3Bwow%26quot%3B%20moment%2C%20but%20said%20he%20also%20believes%20we'll%20need%20more%20breakthroughs%20on%20the%20technical%20side%20to%20reach%20any%20level%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20that%20can%20go%20toe-to-toe%20with%20a%20human%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20says%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20we%20will%20reach%20AGI%20from%20large%20language%20models%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20LLMs%20and%20more%20broadly%20deep%20learning%20are%20probably%20a%20big%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20bet%2C%20the%20biggest%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20we're%20maybe%20missing%20a%20couple%20of%20puzzle%20pieces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrueger%20also%20lays%20blame%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20certain%20AI%20figureheads%20who%20have%20created%20%26quot%3Bunreasonable%20levels%20of%20hype%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20who%20are%20finally%20getting%20a%20reality%20check.%20Altman%20may%20be%20the%20worst%20offender%2C%20but%20he's%20not%20the%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-ai-90-percent-code-3-to-6-months-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epredicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20AI%20would%20be%20writing%2090%25%20of%20software%20developers'%20code%20in%20three%20to%20six%20months.%20The%20actual%20gains%20appear%20to%20be%20much%20more%20modest%3A%20During%20Alphabet's%20Q1%202025%20earnings%20call%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employees-use-ai-or-get-left-behind-gemini-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20code%20written%20at%20Google%20was%20being%20generated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20sort%20of%20feeling%20of%20disappointment%20is%20due%20to%20unreasonable%20levels%20of%20hype%20from%20the%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Krueger.%20As%20the%20rubber%20hits%20the%20road%20and%20the%20breakneck%20speed%20of%20AI%20potentially%20slows%2C%20expectations%20for%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20possible%2C%20maybe%2C%20one%20day%2C%20arrival%20of%20AGI%20%E2%80%94%20are%20finally%20being%20put%20in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20see%20how%20we%20got%20here.%20In%20a%20January%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2025-sam-altman-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Altman%20predicted%20AGI%20would%20arrive%20during%20Trump's%20second%20presidency.%20Elon%20Musk%20once%20predicted%20it%20could%20be%20here%20by%20the%20year's%20end.%20According%20to%20some%20of%20the%20best%20minds%20in%20AI%2C%20AGI%20is%20often%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bfew%20years%20away.%26quot%3B%20In%20truth%20it%20feels%20like%20we're%20finally%20realizing%20nobody%20actually%20knows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20nobody%20has%20had%20more%20of%20a%20humbling%20in%20AI%20than%20Apple%2C%20which%20earlier%20this%20year%20axed%20an%20iPhone%2016%20ad%20that%20promised%20several%20much-hyped%20new%20AI%20features%20that%2C%20as%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20were%20far%20from%20ready.%20When%20Tim%20Cook%20steps%20onstage%20next%20week%2C%20don't%20be%20surprised%20if%20he%20and%20other%20executives%20strike%20a%20more%20measured%20tone%20when%20talking%20about%20AI%2C%20as%20they%20pull%20back%20the%20curtain%20on%20the%20latest%20lineup%20of%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hear%20the%20new%20phone%20will%20be%20a%20little%20thinner%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fhugh-langley%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHugh%20Langley%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20where%20he%20writes%20about%20Google%2C%20tech%2C%20and%20wealth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hype-crashing-into-reality-iphone-openai-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756973821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b88bcb32af4d666ef72db8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hype-crashing-into-reality-iphone-openai-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Between%20Nvidia's%20recent%20earnings%20and%20OpenAI's%20underwhelming%20GPT-5%2C%20it's%20clear%20AI%20is%20entering%20its%20%26quot%3Bmeh%26quot%3B%20era.%20That's%20good%20news%20for%20everyone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40businessinsider.com%20(Hugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hype-crashing-into-reality-iphone-openai-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20Is%20No%20Secret%26quot%3B%3A%20Putin%20On%20His%20Conversation%20With%20PM%20Modi%20During%20Limo%20Ride%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister