Fmother-dairy-to-pass-on-benefits-of-gst-reduction-to-consumers-md-125090400385_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmother-dairy-to-pass-on-benefits-of-gst-reduction-to-consumers-md-125090400385_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Japan%20Airlines%20flights%20from%20Hawaii%20were%20delayed%20up%20to%2018%20hours%20after%20a%20pilot%20for%20one%20of%20the%20flights%20was%20found%20drinking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Japan%20Airlines%20(JAL)%20airplane%20is%20seen%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20International%20Airport%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20Haneda%20Airport%20in%20Tokyo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67580b61dc8b666017f23a4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJapan%20Airlines%20offers%20a%204%2C500%20yen%20luggage%20delivery%20service%20as%20Tokyo%20becomes%20a%20tourist%20hotbed.%3Cp%3EJames%20Matsumoto%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJapan%20Airlines%20flights%20last%20week%20were%20delayed%20after%20a%20pilot%20was%20found%20drinking%20before%20his%20flight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20flights%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20Japan%20were%20delayed%20by%20up%20to%2018%20hours%20because%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20at%20least%20the%20fourth%20case%20of%20a%20Japan%20Airlines%20pilot%20being%20caught%20drinking%20before%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Japan%20Airlines%20flights%20from%20Hawaii%20to%20Japan%20were%20delayed%20up%20to%2018%20hours%20after%20a%20pilot%20was%20found%20drinking%20the%20day%20before%20his%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20pilot%20was%20scheduled%20to%20fly%20JL793%20from%20Honolulu%20to%20Chubu%20Centrair%20International%20Airport%20on%20August%2028.%20Japan%20Airlines%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20pilot%20came%20clean%20about%20drinking%20three%20cans%20of%20beer%20before%20the%20flight%20took%20off.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20that%20the%20captain%20had%20consumed%20three%20cans%20of%20beer%20alone%20in%20the%20hotel%20room%20the%20day%20before%20departure%2C%20and%20was%20deemed%20unfit%20to%20fly.%20A%20replacement%20pilot%20was%20found%20for%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20and%20two%20subsequent%20flights%2C%20headed%20for%20Haneda%20Airport%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20were%20delayed%20by%20around%2018%20hours%20because%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20airline%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20found%20that%20the%20captain%20had%20consumed%20alcohol%20at%20stay%20locations%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20The%20airline%20added%20that%20the%20pilot%20had%20altered%20the%20date%20and%20time%20settings%20of%20the%20alcohol%20detector%20to%20conceal%20results%20in%20previous%20instances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyodo%20News%20reported%20that%20around%20630%20passengers%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20said%20that%20Japanese%20transport%20and%20aviation%20officials%20visited%20Japan%20Airlines'%20headquarters%20in%20Tokyo%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20sincerely%20apologize%20to%20our%20customers%20and%20all%20parties%20involved%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20and%20trouble%20caused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airlines%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20working%20as%20a%20company%20to%20ensure%20the%20thorough%20implementation%20of%20measures%20to%20prevent%20recurrence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20at%20least%20the%20fourth%20case%20of%20a%20Japan%20Airlines%20pilot%20being%20caught%20drinking%20before%20a%20flight%2C%20causing%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20last%20year%2C%20a%20flight%20from%20Dallas%20to%20Tokyo%20was%20canceled%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-flight-canceled-after-pilot-got-drunk-police-called-report-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecaptain%20got%20drunk%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20hotel%20bar%20and%20in%20his%20room.%20The%20Mainichi%20reported%20then%20that%20a%20hotel%20employee%20had%20called%20local%20police%2C%20reporting%20the%20pilot's%20disorderly%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20two%20Japan%20Airlines%20pilots%20were%20suspended%20from%20flying%20for%20drinking%20before%20their%20December%20flight%20from%20Melbourne%20to%20Tokyo%2C%20per%20an%20AFP%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20pilots%20from%20Japan%20Airlines%20that%20have%20been%20found%20drinking%20before%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202024%2C%20a%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20pilot%20was%20jailed%20after%20he%20was%20found%20to%20be%20over%20the%20legal%20alcohol%20limit%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20Edinburgh%20to%20New%20York%20in%20June%202023%2C%20per%20a%20report%20by%20The%20Guardian.%20The%20pilot%20was%20caught%20during%20a%20bag%20search%20at%20Edinburgh%20with%20two%20bottles%20of%20J%C3%A4germeister%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20half%20empty.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20a%20Southwest%20Airlines%20pilot%20who%20was%20due%20to%20fly%20from%20Savannah%2C%20Georgia%2C%20to%20Chicago%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-pilot-charged-dui-police-enter-cockpit-tsa-alcohol-smell-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echarged%20with%20driving%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20influence.%20The%20pilot%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20cockpit%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20landed%20at%20its%20destination%20five%20hours%20after%20its%20scheduled%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Japan%20Airlines%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comm