ion%20laws%2C%20and%20child%20welfare%20committees%20looked%20after%20rehabilitation.%20Police%20and%20sub-divisional%20magistrates%20took%20on%20legal%20duties%20as%20child%20marriage%20prohibition%20officers%2C%20while%20NGOs%2C%20grassroots%20workers%2C%20and%20elected%20village%20representatives%20built%20trust%20in%20communities.%20Academics%20from%20Tripura%20University%20added%20data-driven%20insights%2C%20and%20local%20media%20spread%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20stopped%20working%20in%20silos%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20District%20Magistrate%E2%80%99s%20coordination%20powers%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20unite%20different%20departments%20and%20overcome%20barriers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jaiswal%2C%20the%20urgency%20of%20this%20mission%20was%20never%20abstract%20%E2%80%94%20it%20lived%20in%20the%20stories%20of%20girls%20like%20Sampa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20rescue%20that%20showed%20what%20was%20at%20stake%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESampa%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20from%20Uttar%20Bajapur%2C%20was%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20being%20married%20to%20a%2032-year-old%20man.%20A%20Class%207%20student%2C%20she%20had%20dreams%20of%20studying%20further%2C%20but%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20struggles%20and%20social%20pressures%20pushed%20her%20toward%20a%20different%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Schools%20act%20as%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20with%20a%20protocol%20to%20report%20absences%20that%20might%20indicate%20forced%20marriage.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-5-1756816874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-495383%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchools%20act%20as%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20with%20a%20protocol%20to%20report%20absences%20that%20might%20indicate%20forced%20marriage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2010%20July%202025%2C%20one%20of%20her%20teachers%20noticed%20signs%20of%20the%20impending%20marriage%20and%20called%20Childline.%20Acting%20swiftly%2C%20a%20rescue%20team%20of%20district%20officials%20and%20local%20police%20reached%20her%20home%20and%20intervened%20before%20the%20wedding%20could%20be%20solemnised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20rescued%20a%20day%20before%20the%20wedding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sampa%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20rescue%20team%20came%2C%20I%20felt%20relieved%2C%20and%20I%20told%20them%20I%20was%20being%20married%20without%20my%20consent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20rescue%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20first%20to%20the%20One-Stop%20Centre%20in%20Bishramganj%20(which%20provides%20medical%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20psychological%20support%20to%20women%20in%20distress)%20and%20later%20to%20the%20Sonamura%20SC%20Girls%20Hostel.%20Her%20parents%20signed%20an%20undertaking%20before%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%2C%20promising%20to%20delay%20her%20marriage%20so%20that%20she%20could%20continue%20her%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3