%20to%20the%20family%20running%20the%20pizzeria.%20They%20had%20loved%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20inspired%20my%20answer%20to%20the%20consul%20general.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%20had%20his%20retort%20ready%20%E2%80%94%20Stay%20back%20in%20Brazil%20and%20do%20the%20same!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20couple%20about%20a%20delegation%20of%20150%20Indian%20companies%2C%20part%20of%20a%20trade%20fair%20that%20was%20being%20pioneered%20by%20the%20ITPO%20(India%20Trade%20Promotion%20Organisation)%2C%20that%20would%20be%20docking%20in%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20that%20year.%20Assuring%20them%20of%20all%20support%20from%20the%20consulate%2C%20Tripathi%20asked%20if%20they%20would%20cater%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsamosa-and-company-1756730739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samosa%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20serves%20a%20range%20of%20Indian%20dishes%20that%20have%20been%20inspired%20by%20regions%20across%20the%20subcontinent%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsamosa-and-company-1756730739.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsamosa-and-company-1756730739-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsamosa-and-company-1756730739-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsamosa-and-company-1756730739-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsamosa-and-company-1756730739-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5