iro%20for%20the%20delegation%2C%20and%20cater%20for%20the%20breakfasts%2C%20lunches%20and%20dinners%3B%20it%20was%20just%20Deepali%2C%20me%20and%20two%20helpers.%E2%80%9D%20Everyone%20who%20sampled%20the%20food%20loved%20it.%20And%20out%20of%20the%20earnings%20of%20the%20event%20was%20born%20Samosa%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20that%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20sought%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344409%2Ffomo-momo-food-truck-new-jersey-serves-tandoori-butter-garlic-momos-women-missed-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplace%20Indian%20flavours%20on%20the%20same%20playing%20field%20as%20their%20global%20counterparts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESprucing%20a%20global%20appetite%20for%20Indian%20flavours%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Samosa%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20menu%2C%20a%20bounty%20of%20different%20Indian%20dishes%2C%20each%20originating%20from%20regions%20across%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20vie%20for%20menu%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20the%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20tikki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(potato%20dumplings%20seasoned%20with%20date%20and%20mint%20chutney%20and%20topped%20with%20a%20yoghurt%20sphere)%3B%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20both%20vegetarian%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(filled%20with%20a%20spicy%20mix%20of%20potatoes%2C%20peas%2C%20cashews%2C%20raisins%2C%20herbs%2C%20and%20spices)%20and%20meat%20(filled%20with%20a%20spicy%20mixture%20of%20ground%20goat%20meat%2C%20seasoned%20with%20herbs%20and%20spices)%20versions%3B%20the%20tempura%20%3Cem%3Epakoda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(breaded%20snack%20fried%20in%20chickpea%20flour%20filled%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20seasonal%20vegetables)%3B%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20(fried%20Indian%20roll%20stuffed%20with%20vegetables%3B%20%3Cem%3Edhokla%3C%2Fem%3E%20(made%20with%20chickpea%20flour%2C%20coriander%2C%20cumin%2C%20ginger%2C%20pepper%2